<p>I'm trying to use the sorting mechanism of Zend_Search_Lucene from following documentation: <a href="http://framework.zend.com/manual/en/zend.search.lucene.searching.html#zend.search.lucene.searching.sorting">http://framework.zend.com/manual/en/â€¦</a></p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
